    {
      "text": "A 48-year-old female with a history of rheumatoid arthritis has been taking naproxen for the past 6 months. She presents with epigastric pain, nausea, and dark stools. Upper GI endoscopy reveals a gastric ulcer. What is the drug of choice for managing this condition?",
